data.title: Find the Anagrams
data.statement: Find all the anagrams in a list of N lowercase words.  Some words have multiple anagrams.  Print the anagrams on a line in alphabetical order, and the lines should also be alphabetized.

lastVersion.statementHTML:
Goal

Find all the anagrams in a list of N lowercase words. Some words have multiple anagrams. Print the anagrams on a line in alphabetical order, and the lines should also be alphabetized.
Input
Line 1: Number of words.
Next N lines: The word list.
Output
One line for each set of anagrams. Print the anagrams in alphabetical order, and the lines should also be alphabetized.
Constraints
N ≤ 1000
Example
Input
10
apt
bug
pat
tap
cow
eat
ate
rat
tea
eta
Output
apt pat tap
ate eat eta tea
